  situation  (  is  is  single  not Q  The answer must be a situation when a person with mental illness is able to control their symptoms and lead a normal life. Managed is a word that means to control or handle something, which is relevant to the situation. Effectively treated is also relevant, as it means that the person is getting the right treatment. Recur means to happen again, which is not relevant to the situation. Cause delusion is a word that means to make someone believe something that is not true, which is not relevant to the situation. Illusion is a word that means something that is not real, which is not relevant to the situation. So the answer is managed (a).

